data.description:
Nestled in the heart of a vibrant and thriving community, this charming home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting ambiance. Located Caledonian, 8211 Noble Crest enjoys proximity to a plethora of amenities, including shopping centers, dining options, schools, and recreational facilities. Commuting is a breeze, with easy access to major highways and public transportation routes

Features a spacious and open floor plan that maximizes natural light and promotes a sense of airy tranquility. Gourmet kitchen with upgraded appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage space, making it prefect for any home chef. Large master with an en-suite bathroom. Expansive backyard with well-maintained grass and covered patio, creating an excellent setting for outdoor gatherings and activities. 

Don't miss out on the chance to make 8211 Noble Crest your new address. Schedule a viewing today!
